{"tid":394641,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"fg / 廢青 : 比一年時間試自己有興趣嘅工作?","createTime":"2017-09-10T06:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T15:33:30.000Z","uid":57796,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b645d188e3f14aa040d0c3e55d0ec59138396264","tid":394641,"uid":57796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:42:17.000Z","msg":"有無巴打係過來人講下經驗同依加點?<br />\n<br />\n自己8大CS grad，揾左一個月相關嘅工，但發覺自己唔知想係自己個範度做咩。<br />\n曾經做左3個月IT 狗 full time internship，發覺唔係好like，包括工作環境，內容。<br />\n所以我就諗，不如比D時間做自己有興趣嘅工作先，知道理想同現實係有分別，亦知道如果之後入返IT行，會比人壓同要辛苦地pickup 返D 新野。<br />\n<br />\n家庭唔係問題，只要準時比家用就OK<br />\n<br />\n希望巴打share 經驗 / 比下意見，或者有D野我無考慮到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c91c69cc5471a231d9977cec816af2cd4497b32","tid":394641,"uid":57796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自推"},{"pid":"9e1d42a019386d355628e4d8f5c00c139705be09","tid":394641,"uid":84137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:59:20.000Z","msg":"16GRAD 做左差唔多一年野 想換FIELD"},{"pid":"7b6db010388a075e2b72c3d63ee59c1c7039d380","tid":394641,"uid":52509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T07:02:41.000Z","msg":"介唔介意講你嘅所謂IT係咩POST？"},{"pid":"2000f1b32bc71cffa3d9195f73ddc19d86ab12f3","tid":394641,"uid":57796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T07:06:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>介唔介意講你嘅所謂IT係咩POST？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c5d9fb7a17a3f1bb0ef6360edc2d43f8fb0117","tid":394641,"uid":57796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T07:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>16GRAD 做左差唔多一年野 想換FIELD</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf2bacec6c6caef006a22b09d30deb984c806ba","tid":394641,"uid":44071,"lik