18:02:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果前提係冇大學畢業 又應唔應該試一試？<br />\n為讀而讀既感覺好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀埋先搞啦! 或者一路讀一路做<br />\n走堂淨係考試做pj好快過啦</blockquote><br />\n上堂點名計attendance呢下仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔expect自己會係呢科發奮圖強攞a range<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但求畢業就算"},{"pid":"fc867652afe90fea80aea06e6e1418d8d1d38327","tid":394641,"uid":20582,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T18:12:57.000Z","msg":"我岩岩出黎grad個陣都係咁諗，我都係IT grad, 然後做左兩個月P仔之後走左去影樓做左差唔多一年<br />\n<br />\n我覺得有環境許可試下無壞，無論最後係點，呢一年既經驗同回憶都係自己既，總會有佢既用處。同埋起碼自己試過，無悔，冇機會日後怨自己<br />\n<br />\n利申做返IT狗兩年"},{"pid":"7217af5131a8ef73ff3fedc257f8815afca95609","tid":394641,"uid":52509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我岩岩出黎grad個陣都係咁諗，我都係IT grad, 然後做左兩個月P仔之後走左去影樓做左差唔多一年<br />\n<br />\n我覺得有環境許可試下無壞，無論最後係點，呢一年既經驗同回憶都係自己既，總會有佢既用處。同埋起碼自己試過，無悔，冇機會日後怨自己<br />\n<br />\n利申做返IT狗兩年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你自覺做P有冇天份？"},{"pid":"e4b6537a5be93919c0142f7c6d65e4a0697366ff","tid":394641,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:04:33.000Z","msg":"why not?<br />\n利伸：19歲完夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做左一年唔想再做<br />\n之後再讀書轉行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生活好左，人又健康左"},{"pid":"8515a5d2f87ec19e630430ede02344401c92e8c7","tid":394641,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:10:01.000Z","msg":"無家庭負擔就得<br />\n<br />\n最緊要你有心理準備, 唔好諗住可以搵到同一個人工"},{"pid":"baab4af2cdfd6f096a44ef1ebcfcfe30df23f61c","tid":394641,"uid":62120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c